{"post":{"id":"76b87ea9-9b0b-4fbd-beec-35f555b15276","title":"L’ultime raison qui fait de Lalason un concept unique en son genre","excerpt":"Si vous êtes un créateur de contenu en ligne, que ce soit sur YouTube, Twitch, Instagram ou tout autre plateforme, vous savez...","firstPublishedDate":"2023-06-02T09:03:38.365Z","lastPublishedDate":"2023-06-02T09:03:38.365Z","slug":"plateforme-de-musique-libre-de-droits","featured":false,"pinned":false,"categoryIds":[],"memberId":"b3f3fbbd-9b4e-46c0-b0e4-7edc60705954","hashtags":[],"commentingEnabled":true,"minutesToRead":2,"tagIds":[],"relatedPostIds":[],"pricingPlanIds":[],"language":"fr","richContent":{"nodes":[{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"foo","nodes":[],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"IMAGE","id":"5c4c4","nodes":[],"imageData":{"containerData":{"width":{"size":"CONTENT"},"alignment":"CENTER","textWrap":true},"image":{"src":{"id":"55988d_8bea19f7f0004ed49bae9a04d11ee957~mv2.png"},"width":629,"height":502}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"4fotj","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Si vous êtes un créateur de contenu en ligne, que ce soit sur YouTube, Twitch, Instagram ou tout autre plateforme, vous savez probablement à quel point la musique est importante pour ajouter une touche professionnelle à vos projets. Mais trouver de la musique de qualité qui soit également légale à utiliser peut être difficile et coûteux. C'est là que Lalason entre en jeu.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"172gk","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"​","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"IMAGE","id":"8gv56","nodes":[],"imageData":{"containerData":{"width":{"size":"SMALL"},"alignment":"LEFT","textWrap":true},"image":{"src":{"id":"55988d_abfdc6c95baf4ff6be118c939f8852a9~mv2.png"},"width":748,"height":561}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"3m1h3","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Lalason est une plateforme de musique en ligne qui propose un abonnement mensuel ou annuel donnant accès à une vaste bibliothèque de musique et de sons libres de droits pour une utilisation dans des projets créatifs.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"7efqd","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" ","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"f6utq","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Notre bibliothèque comprend des milliers de pistes de différents genres musicaux, ainsi que des effets sonores, des boucles et des ambiances sonores.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6pif9","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"​","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"ft52o","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Mais ce qui rend Lalason différent des autres plateformes de musique libre de droits, c'est que notre musique est entièrement originale et créée exclusivement pour notre plateforme. Cela signifie que vous ne trouverez pas notre musique sur d'autres plateformes.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"6gahb","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" ","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"aoprm","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"En outre, Lalason travaille en étroite collaboration avec des compositeurs et des artistes français, pour créer notre musique.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"cr3f","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"En choisissant Lalason pour vos besoins musicaux, vous soutenez non seulement une entreprise qui a à cœur de fournir de la musique de qualité pour les créateurs de contenu en ligne, mais vous contribuez également à soutenir la communauté artistique et les compositeurs français.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"9cj92","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"​","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"2kk1d","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"L'abonnement à Lalason est un excellent moyen de soutenir les artistes tout en obtenant de la musique de qualité pour vos projets créatifs en ligne.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"fq10g","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" ","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"IMAGE","id":"9af6a","nodes":[],"imageData":{"containerData":{"width":{"size":"SMALL"},"alignment":"RIGHT","textWrap":true},"image":{"src":{"id":"55988d_d048fc89a354426697ec0609f786485d~mv2.png"},"width":609,"height":618}}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"2t95q","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"C'est une solution pratique, économique et légale pour ajouter de la musique à vos vidéos YouTube, vos émissions Twitch ou vos publications Instagram, tout en soutenant les créateurs qui ont travaillé dur pour produire cette musique.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"10tsl","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":" ","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}},{"type":"PARAGRAPH","id":"42uju","nodes":[{"type":"TEXT","id":"","nodes":[],"textData":{"text":"Alors n'hésitez plus et abonnez-vous dès aujourd'hui à Lalason pour soutenir la communauté artistique et les compositeurs français.","decorations":[{"type":"BOLD","fontWeightValue":700},{"type":"COLOR","colorData":{"foreground":"#ffdeac"}}]}}],"style":{"paddingTop":"0px","paddingBottom":"0px"},"paragraphData":{"textStyle":{"textAlignment":"JUSTIFY"},"indentation":0}}],"metadata":{"version":1,"createdTimestamp":"2024-05-14T09:02:28.203Z","updatedTimestamp":"2024-05-14T09:02:28.203Z","id":"1f9a2741-40e5-45fe-a524-c7af8097f9ac"},"documentStyle":{}},"preview":false,"contentId":"6479b06a52941c49048665ea","mostRecentContributorId":"65b92881-a158-4183-ac86-825e6dbdaf15","media":{"wixMedia":{"image":{"id":"55988d_8bea19f7f0004ed49bae9a04d11ee957~mv2.png","url":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/55988d_8bea19f7f0004ed49bae9a04d11ee957~mv2.png","height":502,"width":629}},"displayed":true,"custom":false},"hasUnpublishedChanges":false,"translations":[],"customExcerpt":false,"internalCategoryIds":[],"internalRelatedPostIds":[]}}